<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>the manifestorium | community</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel:wght@400;700&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { background: #050505; color: #e0e0e0; font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif; }
        .serif { font-family: 'Cinzel', serif; }
        .glass { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }
        .principle { border-left: 2px solid #b026ff; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen pb-24">
    <nav class="fixed top-0 w-full z-50 glass border-b border-white/10">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center">
            <a href="/home.html" class="serif text-xl tracking-widest text-white">THE MANIFESTORIUM</a>
            <div class="hidden md:flex gap-8 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase">
                <a href="/store.html" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Artifacts</a>
                <a href="/community.html" class="text-cyan-400">Community</a>
                <a href="/faq.html" class="hover:text-cyan-400">FAQ</a>
                <a href="/contact.html" class="hover:text-cyan-400">Contact</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <main class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="serif text-5xl mb-4 text-center">Community & Exchange</h1>
        <p class="text-center text-gray-500 mb-16">How we operate in Slab City. No money required for everything.</p>

        <div class="space-y-16">
            <section>
                <h2 class="serif text-2xl text-purple-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">The Non-Monetary Exchange</h2>
                <div class="glass p-8 rounded-lg">
                    <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                        We believe in circular economies. If you have no currency but possess skills, materials, 
                        or stories, we may still trade. The Manifestorium operates on a dual-track system.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                        <div class="principle pl-6">
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Accepted Materials</h3>
                            <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-1">
                                <li>Copper wire (uncoated)</li>
                                <li>Quartz crystals (clear or rose)</li>
                                <li>Reclaimed wood (palm preferred)</li>
                                <li>Functional solar cells</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div class="principle pl-6">
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Accepted Skills</h3>
                            <ul class="text-gray-400 text-sm space-y-1">
                                <li>Welding / Metalwork</li>
                                <li>Electrical engineering</li>
                                <li>Documentary photography</li>
                                <li>Desert agriculture</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2 class="serif text-2xl text-cyan-400 mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">Slab City Standards</h2>
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="glass p-6 rounded-lg flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <span class="text-2xl">1.</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Leave No Trace (Except Art)</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Pack out everything. The desert is not your landfill. If you build here, build beautifully.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass p-6 rounded-lg flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <span class="text-2xl">2.</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Water is Sacred</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">We operate on a communal water share. If you visit, bring water or donate to the community fund.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass p-6 rounded-lg flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <span class="text-2xl">3.</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Respect the Range</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">The Navy owns the sky here. Don't interfere with their exercises, and they won't interfere with ours.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="glass p-6 rounded-lg flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <span class="text-2xl">4.</span>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Portal Protocol</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Never enter a portal alone. Always announce your intentions to the room. No flash photography inside.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section class="text-center py-12 border-t border-white/10">
                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">Want to join the community?</p>
                <a href="/contact.html" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 border border-white/30 text-white uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition">
                    Propose an Exchange
                </a>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
